    "name": "遗民天境",
    "steam_appid": 2134390,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你醒啦，这是一个充满悬浮岛屿的神秘世界，这里的天空泛着微光，岛屿如同破碎的梦境般漂浮在空中，周围都是陌生的植被和未知的生态系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你渐渐适应了这里的规则，建设家园，发展科技，从零开始，从原始的工具到先进的机械，制造科技造物，探索未知的岛屿，寻找其他幸存者，探索这个奇异世界的生成原因，解开来到这里的原因，寻找回家的路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎通过以下官方平台关注我们，获取最新消息，并与我们面对面交流：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>B站：@遗民天境</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小黑盒：@遗民天境</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>小红书：@遗民天境</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>QQ群：903506424</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为了方便您的反馈，更多的交流反馈渠道持续开拓中</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >期待你的加入！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/5215fe2e349dbdc23857c78e02882321.avif?t=1772072375\" width=494 height=104 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要想富先砍树，你可以通过采集资源点，开启资源箱获取大量资源，所有资源都是文明升级的基础燃料，没有资源积累，发展将寸步难行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/8862b14f06e266f7680c526ddf4d4be9.poster.avif?t=1772072375\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/8862b14f06e266f7680c526ddf4d4be9.webm?t=1772072375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/8862b14f06e266f7680c526ddf4d4be9.mp4?t=1772072375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/4a88c9fe64434e2dc6200f58f235329f.avif?t=1772072375\" width=494 height=104 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >家园的发展离不开合理的规划。你需要合理分配人手，制定生产任务。将原始资源转化为精密工业品。规划高效工业区，合理布局设施构建生产网络，用机器之力突破生产力瓶颈，推动科技树向未来延伸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/b8c14bb2735ba8e4550733dff281184c.poster.avif?t=1772072375\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/b8c14bb2735ba8e4550733dff281184c.webm?t=1772072375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/b8c14bb2735ba8e4550733dff281184c.mp4?t=1772072375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/3b671e5d88c6aa32d43b50172bd6e1f5.avif?t=1772072375\" width=494 height=104 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在空岛上你可以自由搭建房间和设施，用你的巧思和创意将荒芜空岛建设成拥有工业区、生态区、生活区的空中家园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/9549392a495cfbcf8ab609c6d4da71e1.poster.avif?t=1772072375\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/9549392a495cfbcf8ab609c6d4da71e1.webm?t=1772072375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/9549392a495cfbcf8ab609c6d4da71e1.mp4?t=1772072375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/04f6017c51518aeba6e28c4edb8c6ad8.avif?t=1772072375\" width=494 height=104 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在对空岛的探索中，遗民们发现了一种天然辉石，其内部蕴藏着巨大的能量。只需巧妙地将其发射的幽波引导至关键之处，便能唤醒沉睡的机器，让它们自行运转，彻底解放遗民的双手。然而，这远不是幽波之力的极限，还有更多的可能等待你去探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/fff61b6317478df15cc089ea51068b9f.poster.avif?t=1772072375\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/fff61b6317478df15cc089ea51068b9f.webm?t=1772072375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/fff61b6317478df15cc089ea51068b9f.mp4?t=1772072375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/a5c78f264a0f53d87c8656c7fe73fd8d.avif?t=1772072375\" width=494 height=104 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色的移动速度太慢？工作效率太低怎么办？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别担心，可以通过穿着装备、使用神像、激发特殊技能等方式强化角色能力，提升角色工作效率，让每一次行动都更加快捷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/1b1f83318220d065f64de1801dd39d75.poster.avif?t=1772072375\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/1b1f83318220d065f64de1801dd39d75.webm?t=1772072375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/1b1f83318220d065f64de1801dd39d75.mp4?t=1772072375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/c58d3fbc99a76febacc985299001b3cf.avif?t=1772072375\" width=494 height=104 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索世界是游戏的重要组成部分，游戏中有多种区域供你探索，每一种区域都是独特的生态圈，蕴藏着丰富的资源和无限机遇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/3bfcf7649641670e3bb6591df0e0d002.poster.avif?t=1772072375\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/3bfcf7649641670e3bb6591df0e0d002.webm?t=1772072375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/3bfcf7649641670e3bb6591df0e0d002.mp4?t=1772072375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134390/extras/7352efe2ec09b94695750d0b360d180b.avif?t=1772072375\" width=494 height=140 /></span></p>",
